title: GDP rose 0.2% in June qtr
text:
Wed, Sep 2, 2015, 11:39 AM AEST - Australia Markets close in 4 hrs 21 mins GDP rose 0.2% in June qtr AAP – 7 minutes ago 
Australia's economy grew by 0.2 per cent in the June quarter and by 2.0 per cent over the 12 months to June, official figures show.
